data.value:
With this tool you can flash firmwares for both Teensy & Wemos hardwares. These firmware are used with DirectOutput to trigger adressable leds effects.
Thsi tool is using two CLI flashers for both Teensy & Wemos.
https://github.com/espressif/esptool https://github.com/PaulStoffregen/teensy_loader_cli
This tool is used in the Arnoz Tiny Tools suite
